Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the \Nprize for a fighting event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the Flare-Flare Fruit, \Nhe decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burgess from the Blackbeard Pirates won\Nthe match of Block A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the battle of Block B has begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Law and the others are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tra-guy!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to change the handing-over spot now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already here. Stop making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm worried about the situation of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their king quit all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come they are so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in unexpected circumstances already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what worries me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a barrier human who ate \Nthe Barrier-Barrier Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of Block B is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Fighting Fish Strike!\NAcross the Deadly Iron Bridge!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's clear, the battle of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Block B ended with Bartolomeo as its winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strange guy won after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant old pops and Cabbage are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Move!\N--You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cheer me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\i1}you{\i0} have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You now use Haki that's far greater\Nthan anyone can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pride has been broken to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... S... S... S...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:18.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,45 MINUTES BEFORE THE HANDOVER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CAESAR HANDOVER TEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... It's a very solid-looking bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay if that Fighting Fish thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attacks us on this, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, don't tell me \Nyou're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What is that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It showed itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought a Fighting Fish would be a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call that a fish!\NIt's no different from a sea monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is more than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy said they reinforced the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with iron to protect it from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's going to be alright, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is a piece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we make it to Green Bit like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You handle it, Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack - Green Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one from the opposite side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna crush us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Bombgrass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not!\NCan't you see how many there are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just run!\NIt'll take forever to fight them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Bombgrass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nose-{\i1}ya{\i0}, uncuff Caesar!\NI want him to fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!\NHe's gonna fly away then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't dare make a move like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't die a peaceful death...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after pushing around a \Ngreat scientist like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastille!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's so powerful!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a criminal with a 300 million \Nberry bounty could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastille!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, why aren't you fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't just make me fight all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes so much energy to use my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have to be at my best on our way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDo you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my strength up\Nas much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because our enemy is Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law... Is he really going \Nto fight against Joker?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I can't see the other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,side clearly because of the fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fighting Fish is coming towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't let it destroy \Nanymore of the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We caught it!\N--Alright, let's pull it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a decisive battle today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat Fighting Fish stew \Nto boost up our energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's voice is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Residents of the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a deserted island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who is over there on the other side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to cross the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It's a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly us to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, you bastard!\NI'll get even with you, I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a view! What a lovely view!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have flown ourselves \Nlike this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much gas energy do you think \Nyou need to fly three people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an important hostage for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:03.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE DESERTED ISLAND NORTH OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drag marks from the fish end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipwrecks from Fighting Fish attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nare filling up the water around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:23.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GREEN BIT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:20.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A very wild forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the battle of Block C!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will commence shortly\Nafter they finish fixing the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:16:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All competitors of Block C,\Nplease go to the entrance gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's about time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat! All competitors of Block C,\Nplease go to the entrance gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let me introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the competitors who everyone \Nshould keep an eye on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the two-time champion of\Nthe New World Central Fighting Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Destruction Cannon" Ideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are savage assassins \Nwho are able to kill pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with more than a 100 million bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Funk Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is from the famous \NGiants' country - Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most formidable "Pirate Mercenary"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Known for his violence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which he uses in order to drive \Nhis target into the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean the Bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can stop this bull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum's Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brutal Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's likely winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gang from the Kano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the legendary former \Npirate - Don Chinjao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also a lot more tough contenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be an exciting match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle of Block C will \Nbe a very fierce one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NGet ready for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little while ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the "next town" over in Dressrosa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a bad idea! Why don't you go back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}, I must've been out of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible I was to ask you such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask you to kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I ask you such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NEven though you're quite a strong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just walk away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the man is in that storage room,\Ndidn't you, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna ask me why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask you why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the reason I want you to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing your tears is good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of everything and be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have your last cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a few minutes to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the asshole\Nwho makes Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0} cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So that woman asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She shouldn't be fooled by a crumb like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill that son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What did you say?!\N--Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oeil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flanchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poitrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party Table Kick Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your filthy hands off of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want me to kill her,\Nyou better not move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NWhere... Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive a man like you\Nwho makes a woman cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amour Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our love!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}, I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not hurt, are you, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would do anything for you, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...die for me, "Black Foot" Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? V-Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
